Package: NetLit
Title: Augment a literature review with network analysis statistics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Devin",
           family = "Judge-Lord",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "devinjudgelord@fas.harvard.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4384-4380"))
Description: This package takes in a dataframe where each row is a relationship between concepts (an edgelist). Various functions produce common summary statistics of networks. The aim is to aid literature reviews with network analysis statistics.
